## 📘 About the Course

This course introduces high school students to the fundamentals of **Python programming**. Over 6 weeks, students will explore:
- Variables and Data Types
- Strings, Lists, Tuples, Dictionaries
- Conditional Statements and Loops
- Functions
- File Handling and JSON
- Mini Projects

